rComments: She pushes her opinion on her students and she can be very passive aggressive and rude.

The class rocks and Ethel is approachable and professional. It's great to have someone who teaches us the academic and the practical side of public policy.  I am learning so much and I feel like this really helps me decide whether I want to work in public policy.  Lectures are always fun. I have visited her office hours and she is always eager to help.
